{
  "text": "To verify that conservation of the 110 bp fragment after Hae III digestion was not due to the presence of inhibitors of the enzyme in the tumour tissue, two amplified P53 samples were sequenced by Sanger's method using Vent DNA polymerase (Biolab) [CITATION_1] and 33PdATP [CITATION_2] . The same set of sense and antisense primers utilised for DNA amplification by PCR were used as sequencing primers.",
  "citation_candidates": [
